ygData.messageBody:
Skull of Jhen 'Tra can be found off the Gnoll embalmer at nite at Lake rathne. It has a pet with it... ice skele , zombies and undead gnoll will be around for the party. More stuff could be found of the embalmers, sometimes. one time i got 4 items, skull (20 mana and 8sv), a stone, Polished bone earring(10mana) and a weapon.

BiBi
Druiding at Kelethin
(formerly known as the Kick Ass, wise , trusted, highly Valued, Good guy Monk..YiYang)..bow
